{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B33ThemeAlertComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of alert"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSAlert","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"AlertComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the compone